        {
            "title": "西甲｜安東尼連扭2人助攻領貝迪斯贏波 隊友大讚係天才 但完場前領紅被逐(有片)",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/61dd68d7105bc67dbe6c8f285d24c3d0/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250224/_2025022412093785178.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曼聯棄將安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻！安東尼於周日西甲延續勇態，在快攻中連過兩關後助攻伊斯高建功，連續3場西甲有份炮製入球，助球隊作客2:1擊敗基達菲，賽後獲伊斯高大讚是天才球員。不過，安東尼完場前魯莽犯規直紅被逐，下場將無緣鬥皇家馬德里。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼馬菲奧斯完場前領紅。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/466d3e21c8687677be047edc3c5c4d79/2025-02/GettyImages-2201532734_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼馬菲奧斯完場前領紅。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼馬菲奧斯完場前領紅。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3ec58eead364c65189ebd236f2e38421/2025-02/GettyImages-2201533581.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼馬菲奧斯完場前領紅。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯2:1基達菲。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb71bfe3bb4ad360e26ff52c15e3c2f7/2025-02/GettyImages-2201530263.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯2:1基達菲。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼馬菲奧斯完場前領紅。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ff17bc893b5ade599af5fde318636ede/2025-02/GettyImages-2201532939.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼馬菲奧斯完場前領紅。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1bbf08c05bc12939447bd52ae8fa99e3/2025-02/2025-02-20T191550Z_969049703_UP1EL2K1HICTJ_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-BET-GNT-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4344204bcf4fd02c340bc4874b1b8442/2025-02/2025-02-20T183859Z_988034743_UP1EL2K1FSYSC_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-BET-GNT-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/94e633bd6e811856f140ab6cf4ca1968/2025-02/2025-02-20T181419Z_1763486749_UP1EL2K1ENTR8_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-BET-GNT-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼馬菲奧斯又助攻。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>安東尼連扭2人交助攻</h2>\n<p>在曼聯被稱為超級水貨的安東尼自外借加盟貝迪斯後即翻生，今場他又有貨交，於第17分鐘一次快速反擊中，由後場高速推進，期間連過兩關，然後再交出美妙直線予伊斯高射入開紀錄，最終協助球隊作客2:1擊敗基達菲。\n\n</p><h2>相關片段：</h2>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">Antony with an incredible assist today. Making it 5 G/A in five games 🔥🔥🔥 <a href=\"https://t.co/nixYFRCRRo\">pic.twitter.com/nixYFRCRRo</a>\n— Prince 👑 (@Princeutd1P) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Princeutd1P/status/1893721787508068590?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 23, 2025</a></p></blockquote>\n<script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\"></script>\n<h2>隊友大讚是天才</h2>\n<p>今場再有助攻後，這名巴西國腳已經連續3場西甲有份參與入球，共貢獻入球和助攻和2次，於各賽事為貝迪斯上陣6場收穫3入球2助攻。因此，伊斯高大讚這位新隊友道：「與安東尼一起踢球十分輕鬆，他天賦異禀，總是能做出正確的決定。很高興能全取3分，我們要繼續努力。」\n\n</p><h2>領紅無緣鬥皇馬</h2>\n<p>不過，戰至補時階段時，安東尼因一次從後攔截而直接領紅被逐，為勝利添上陰影。更重要的是，貝迪斯下場將主場大戰皇家馬德里，此子缺陣勢嚴重打擊球隊，有不少網民也大感可惜，笑言很想看安東尼大戰基利安麥巴比。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054568/即時-體育-西甲-安東尼連扭2人助攻領貝迪斯贏波-隊友大讚係天才-但完場前領紅被逐-有片",
